  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'The undead seem to be too co-ordinated to be acting randomly.


      They
      must be under the control of a master.'
    nextOption: Yes, we should put together a team to...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'No need for that.


      While you are over at the graveyard,
      do some reconnaisance.


      See if you can find any really tough looking
      ones.'
    nextOption: And report back to you right?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Exactly!


      Right after you''ve dealt with it!'
    nextOption: So go take out a bunch of undead by myself?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'That''s the spirit!


      Now you''re getting the idea.'
    nextOption: Sure, I've got this... I think...
